{
  "stem": "1775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Enough is enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "My husband decided differently.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "When one of the boys-- when we went in into that particular train, train thing, the Germans knocked the biggest nails into-- with lumber to close up the little window because it was boxcars for cows and things that they transport.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And they closed up all those, those little windows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the men took off a piece of lumber from around the boxcar in the middle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They took off the piece of lumber to knock out the nails with the thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they were able to do it, and they did it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And one of the boys went out through the little window and unlocked the door from the-- from the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And when he unlocked the door from the train, people started to jump.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And my husband said, come jump.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I'm just giving up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I'm not doing-- I can't do it no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I'm, I'm-- that's, that's the end, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I can't-- I can't do it no more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "He says, come look what the other people are doing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Just come and look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Everybody kept pushing me and pushing me and pushing me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "By the time I realized, I was by the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And before I could say anything, he just pushed me out and jumped after me, my husband.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then he picked me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I looked at him, and he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what are we going to do now?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we started to walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we walked back to the ghetto again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was very few people left at that time in the ghetto, very few, legally, maybe about 150, maybe 200 at the most.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
